item.title: Lil help with testscape plz
item.dc:creator: @Splid Splid
item.description:
@Splid wrote:

Ok, to start off, if you don’t know what client.java is, you have much to learn. Its one of the main files in your server source that links all of your other source files together. You can’t miss it, it opens with wordpad normally.

And for the people that you can’t train at ::wildtrain, there is also some people that you can’t trade at ardougne. I had this problem with my source, but i found a fix for this bug, i’ll get you a link to this bugfix and then add it to my post.

Good luck.[br][size=1]Posted at: August 09, 2006, 05:38:41 AM[/size][hr]http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,7262.0.html
